# Dr. Lisa Simon Website - Technical Overview

## Project Summary
Professional Hebrew website for Dr. Lisa Simon, a clinical psychologist. Single-page scrolling layout with tab-based navigation.

## Tech Stack

### Frontend
- **Framework:** Next.js 15+ (App Router, TypeScript)
- **Styling:** Tailwind CSS v4
- **Language:** Hebrew (RTL)
- **Font:** Heebo (Google Fonts, weights: 300, 400, 500, 600, 700)

### Backend
- **Database:** Supabase (Postgres)
- **API:** Next.js API Routes (`/app/api/contact/route.ts`)
- **Form Handling:** react-hook-form + zod validation

### Deployment
- **Platform:** Vercel
- **Build:** Static generation for main page, dynamic API route

## Project Structure
```
/app
  ├── layout.tsx          # Root layout (RTL, Heebo font, SEO metadata)
  ├── page.tsx            # Main page (all sections)
  ├── globals.css         # Tailwind config, color palette, smooth scroll
  └── api/contact/route.ts # Form submission endpoint

/components
  ├── Navigation.tsx      # Sticky tab navigation with active state
  ├── ScrollSection.tsx   # Section wrapper for smooth scroll anchoring
  └── ContactForm.tsx     # Contact form with validation

/sections
  ├── HomeSection.tsx     # Hero/intro
  ├── TherapySection.tsx  # Therapy services
  ├── AboutSection.tsx    # About Dr. Simon
  ├── AcademicSection.tsx # Research background
  ├── LecturesSection.tsx # Public lectures
  └── ContactSection.tsx  # Contact info + form

/lib
  ├── supabase.ts         # Supabase client initialization
  └── contactSchema.ts    # Zod validation schema for contact form

/context
  ├── technical-overview.md # This file
  └── product-brief.md      # Product requirements
```

## Key Features

### RTL Support
- `dir="rtl"` on `<html>` element
- Hebrew language (`lang="he"`)
- Tailwind RTL-aware utilities
- Line-height optimized for Hebrew: 1.75 for body, 1.3 for headings

### Navigation
- 6 tabs: בית, טיפול, אודות, מחקר, הרצאות, יצירת קשר
- Smooth scroll to anchored sections
- Active state detection on scroll
- Mobile: hamburger menu with slide-down animation

### Contact Form
- Fields: name, email, phone (optional), message
- Client-side validation with Zod
- Hebrew error messages
- API route validates and inserts to Supabase
- Success/error states with auto-dismiss

### Design System

**Color Palette:**
- Background: `#fafaf8` (off-white/cream)
- Foreground: `#2d2d2d` (dark charcoal)
- Primary: `#e5dfd5` (warm beige)
- Accent: `#7fa99b` (muted teal/sage)

**Typography:**
- Font: Heebo
- Body: 16-18px, line-height 1.75
- Headings: Responsive scale, line-height 1.3

**Spacing:**
- Consistent vertical rhythm
- Section padding: large (py-20 on desktop)
- Content max-width: 6xl (1280px)

## Database Schema

**Table:** `contact_submissions`
```sql
CREATE TABLE contact_submissions (
  id UUID DEFAULT gen_random_uuid() PRIMARY KEY,
  name TEXT NOT NULL,
  email TEXT NOT NULL,
  phone TEXT,
  message TEXT NOT NULL,
  created_at TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT NOW() NOT NULL
);
```

**Row Level Security:**
- Public can INSERT (submit forms)
- Public cannot SELECT (read submissions)

